headline: Pringles® Canada Continues its Partnership with Movember to Spark Conversations and Champion Men's Mental Health
summary: For the second year in a row, Pringles® Canada is partnering with Movember – the world's leading men's health charity – to help raise awareness and spark meaningful dialogue about men's mental health. During the month of Movember, Pringles® will donate up to $50,000 and is launching an engaging social media campaign to foster meaningful conversations around men's mental health.
